  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Are you ready for a new battle? Our enemies are not all fools, so don't die easily!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Background</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the accident was prevented a few years ago, alien enemies soon invaded the earth and supported several puppet regimes to control us humans. As an experienced former agent, you will help the resistance organization launch an attack on the minions of the invaders and thwart one of their evil plans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/f2db506b5e004814093ba8be1ef10a4e.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/f2db506b5e004814093ba8be1ef10a4e.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a classic third-person shooter game. You can press 1, 2, and 3 to switch guns. Press the left mouse button to draw your gun and shoot immediately when in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/f63025dddd3e09e2566e01eaa7048885.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/f63025dddd3e09e2566e01eaa7048885.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/e73a9832a6b5cdf58271aee588658423.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/e73a9832a6b5cdf58271aee588658423.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the password-finding and door-opening accident in the first game, this game also adds the lock-picking puzzle process. The lock's difficulty is divided into easy, medium, and difficult. Remember, pay attention to the swing of the hairpin. If it moves, it means success is not far away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.poster.avif?t=1737891348\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.webm?t=1737891348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.mp4?t=1737891348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About the new quest system</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will get quests in both active and passive ways. That is, when you pass through a door, or talk to a specific NPC and interact with an item, a new task will be opened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/0a66703fd86bb4a0fbd09153eef1bb49.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/0a66703fd86bb4a0fbd09153eef1bb49.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game adds side quests. If you want to switch quests, press <strong><i>ESC</i></strong> to open the comprehensive information page to make a selection. You can also see the ongoing, completed, and failed quests. Of course, you can choose to skip certain quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/e2b75698dbcfcd4ab9bc49331f01a13e.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/e2b75698dbcfcd4ab9bc49331f01a13e.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>At Last</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry about ammunition, the undercover agents of the resistance organization have provided you with plenty of ammo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/cc3dcec8c47037c6a2900719e9acce25.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/cc3dcec8c47037c6a2900719e9acce25.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to fly a mecha? You can try to fly a humanoid mecha in this game. Finally, I wish you good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/3b2bbbb3c6148e99eaf05134f4a7d9d7.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/3b2bbbb3c6148e99eaf05134f4a7d9d7.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Are you ready for a new battle? Our enemies are not all fools, so don't die easily!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Background</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although the accident was prevented a few years ago, alien enemies soon invaded the earth and supported several puppet regimes to control us humans. As an experienced former agent, you will help the resistance organization launch an attack on the minions of the invaders and thwart one of their evil plans.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/f2db506b5e004814093ba8be1ef10a4e.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/f2db506b5e004814093ba8be1ef10a4e.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a classic third-person shooter game. You can press 1, 2, and 3 to switch guns. Press the left mouse button to draw your gun and shoot immediately when in danger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/f63025dddd3e09e2566e01eaa7048885.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/f63025dddd3e09e2566e01eaa7048885.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/e73a9832a6b5cdf58271aee588658423.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/e73a9832a6b5cdf58271aee588658423.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the password-finding and door-opening accident in the first game, this game also adds the lock-picking puzzle process. The lock's difficulty is divided into easy, medium, and difficult. Remember, pay attention to the swing of the hairpin. If it moves, it means success is not far away.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.poster.avif?t=1737891348\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.webm?t=1737891348\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/9c3980ccd0f0d619a889a153425b867c.mp4?t=1737891348\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About the new quest system</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this game, you will get quests in both active and passive ways. That is, when you pass through a door, or talk to a specific NPC and interact with an item, a new task will be opened.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/0a66703fd86bb4a0fbd09153eef1bb49.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/0a66703fd86bb4a0fbd09153eef1bb49.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game adds side quests. If you want to switch quests, press <strong><i>ESC</i></strong> to open the comprehensive information page to make a selection. You can also see the ongoing, completed, and failed quests. Of course, you can choose to skip certain quests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/e2b75698dbcfcd4ab9bc49331f01a13e.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/e2b75698dbcfcd4ab9bc49331f01a13e.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>At Last</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't worry about ammunition, the undercover agents of the resistance organization have provided you with plenty of ammo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/cc3dcec8c47037c6a2900719e9acce25.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/cc3dcec8c47037c6a2900719e9acce25.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to fly a mecha? You can try to fly a humanoid mecha in this game. Finally, I wish you good luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras/3b2bbbb3c6148e99eaf05134f4a7d9d7.avif?t=1737891348\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3373730/extras_big/3b2bbbb3c6148e99eaf05134f4a7d9d7.avif?t=1737891348 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
